window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The deeper they delve, the higher the stakes.</b></p> <p>Harald and the Throne Hunters have ascended—stronger, sharper, and far more dangerous. But so too have their enemies. With the Fallen Angel's dungeon twisting into stranger shapes, and Flutic spiralling toward open war, the crew must decide what they stand for… and what they're willing to sacrifice.</p> <p>Old ghosts rise. Alliances fracture. And the Twilight Crown has begun to whisper.</p> <p>Victory may grant power beyond imagining. But only if they survive.</p>"; 
